    Generate and Construct All PTMs Network

    GenerateAndConstructptmsNetwork.Rd

    This function generates and constructs the PTMs network from given data lists and tables.

    GenerateAndConstructptmsNetwork(
  eu_ptms_list,
  sp_ptms_list,
  sed_ptms_list,
  ptmtable,
  keeplength = 2,
  output_dir = "plots"
)

    Arguments

    eu_ptms_list

    A list containing all PTMs data for the Euclidean distance calculation.

    sp_ptms_list

    A list containing all PTMs data for the Spearman dissimilarity calculation.

    sed_ptms_list

    A list containing all PTMs data for the average of the Euclidean and Spearman distance calculations.

    ptmtable

    A data frame containing all PTMs data.

    keeplength

    An integer specifying the minimum length of common elements to keep. Default is 2.

    output_dir

    A string specifying the output directory for saving plots. Default is "plots".

    Value

    A list containing the updated ptmtable and data for eu.sp.sed.ptms.
